    "MissionGiver": "InterSec Defense Solutions",
    "Title": "Retrieve Additional Smuggler Intel",
    "Description": "MISSION SPECS\n\nArea of Operation: Nyx System\nHostile Forces: Outlaws present and armed\nEquipment Specs: Combat-rated Ship, Personal Arms\nBriefing: InterSec needs your services once again.\n\nThe intel you previously gathered has been invaluable in identifying several prominent buyers of the illegally-obtained Vanduul parts. However, since then the Shattered Blade have continued their operations and the UEE is requesting that we <EM4>update our intel.</EM4>\n\nWe believe more information can be retrieved from the storage facilities located at the old <EM4>QV Logistics station.</EM4>\n\nThe operation parameters haven\u2019t changed since your last mission: find the <EM4>encrypted data</EM4> and use the <EM4>decryption key</EM4> to decipher and upload the list to us. The Shattered Blade will have reinforced the area since the last time, so expect resistance.\n\nGood luck. We\u2019ll be in touch.\n\n\nRespectfully,\n\nDeacon Tobin\nOperations Manager\nInterSec Defense Solutions\n\nThis communication consists of confidential information solely intended for the recipient. Please disregard if received in error and notify sender. All operations are conducted at the contractor\u2019s own personal risk and must adhere to UEE and system law where applicable.",
